{"tid":2390750,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎放低你嘅傷感，重新出發","createTime":"2021-02-01T18:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T19:34:19.000Z","uid":344623,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15fbfb3a5cb33a0bbd215cc048c2ee763dfaa3b8","tid":2390750,"uid":344623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T18:46:26.000Z","msg":"應承自己用一年時間慢慢放低段關係，<br />\n<br />\n放開錯嘅人，<br />\n<br />\n先能夠有空位俾更適合嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n有啲野捉得愈緊愈容易失去，<br />\n<br />\n學識唔再強求，<br />\n<br />\n放過自己，<br />\n<br />\n先能夠遇到對的人。<br />\n<br />\n一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢係對的人，<br />\n<br />\n要相信係你嘅點兜兜轉轉都會翻黎你身邊，<br />\n<br />\n就當分開吓俾大家各自成長。<br />\n<br />\n所以就算分手好傷感，<br />\n<br />\n都要努力過好每一日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e17fb2dd276042a7a7640fe70525cf3f9ae02b","tid":2390750,"uid":343385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T18:51:16.000Z","msg":"以為佢係對的人，但原來佢已經遠去"},{"pid":"f7b6473542e9145652547535d47fb55c7ed4cddd","tid":2390750,"uid":183308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T18:52:56.000Z","msg":"放開左 但未放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ad4bc92ed3ad6169b5085168fb2566cc7249a2","tid":2390750,"uid":344623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68e17fb2dd276042a7a7640fe70525cf3f9ae02b","tid":2390750,"uid":343385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T18:51:16.000Z","msg":"以為佢係對的人，但原來佢已經遠去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:18:54.000Z","msg":"學識放手，<br />\n<br />\n時間會話你知到底佢係咪對的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16404b16cf157d363f758c3cdbfdad84525ea0e","tid":2390750,"uid":344623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7b6473542e9145652547535d47fb55c7ed4cddd","tid":2390750